Summary: cone shape moving changing direction rapid motion.
divs: Sighting DetailsIt was during a thunder storm but storm was in the distance no where near event. fast moving cone shape light changing direction, seen it twice was waiting for a third time so I could get a picture but did not occur, second event was 5 seconds after first, my first thought was it looked like a light tornado in the sky, the light followed it self in a pulsating fashion as it moved very unnatural looking that is why I am posting this. sky was clear I can see the stars in the area where it happened, the lightning was far to the left miles away.
